>> servings: 2

Cook @Rice{2.5%cup} with some @Salt{1.5%tbsp} and keep it aside.

Cut some @Onions{1} into long slices.

Take a pan and add some @Oil{2%tbsp} and Onions into it. Fry till golden.

Add @Salt{1%tbsp} and @Chilly Powder{2%tbsp} into the pan and mix.

Add @Puliogre Mix{4%tbsp} to the pan and dry in medium heat for 3 mins.

Mix it with @Boiled Rice{3%cups} in the end.
